<h1>Service Agreement (English)</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated: 2025-11-23</strong></p>

<h2>1. Scope & Services</h2>
<ul>
    <li>The App provides AI-powered insurance debate simulation, persona-based comments, status display, and history saving.</li>
    <li>The App does not offer financial/insurance sales or advice; all content is for reference only.</li>
</ul>

<h2>2. Account & Use</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Guest mode is supported; phone login is under development/testing.</li>
    <li>You are responsible for lawful use; do not use the App for illegal, infringing, or improper purposes.</li>
    <li>If you notice abnormal use of your account/device ID, stop using and contact us in-app.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Minors</h2>
<ul>
    <li>This App is not intended for users under 13. If you are a minor, please use the App under the supervision of a guardian and avoid submitting personal information.</li>
    <li>We do not knowingly collect data from minors. If a guardian believes a minor has used the App without permission, please contact us for remediation.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Model Content & Responsibility</h2>
<ul>
    <li>AI-generated debate/comment content may be inaccurate, outdated, or biased; please judge on your own.</li>
    <li>Generated content does not represent the App or developers; we are not liable for decisions or losses based on it.</li>
</ul>

<h2>AI Content & Responsibility (Enhanced)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>AI-generated debates, comments, and opinions are produced algorithmically and may be inaccurate, outdated, biased, illogical, or inappropriate.</li>
    <li>We make no warranties regarding their accuracy, reliability, completeness, or suitability.</li>
    <li>You assume full responsibility for any decisions or actions based on such content; the App and developers are not liable for resulting losses.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4. Data & Storage</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Local: your topics, persona configs, and histories are stored on-device; you can delete them in-app.</li>
    <li>Requests are proxied to model providers; avoid entering sensitive information.</li>
</ul>

<h2>5. Permissions</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Photo library write is requested only when saving a debate poster; denying it does not affect other features.</li>
    <li>No access to contacts, location, etc., unrelated to core functions.</li>
</ul>

<h2>6. Prohibited Uses</h2>
<ul>
    <li>No illegal, infringing, malicious, spam, or abusive behavior.</li>
    <li>No reverse engineering, scraping, bulk abuse, or bypassing security controls.</li>
</ul>

<h2>7. Changes & Suspension</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Features/models/endpoints may change or be suspended; continued use means acceptance of changes.</li>
    <li>If service is stopped, we will notify as legally or technically feasible.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Changes & Suspension (Enhanced)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>We may modify, suspend, or restrict access to the services for legal, risk control, model updates, technical reasons, or other reasonable causes.</li>
    <li>Where feasible, notice will be provided; continued use means acceptance.</li>
</ul>

<h2>8. Disclaimer</h2>
<ul>
    <li>We are not liable for interruptions, data loss, or content deviations caused by network, devices, third parties (e.g., model providers), or force majeure.</li>
    <li>You are responsible for your device/network security.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Disclaimer (Enhanced)</h2>
<ul>
    <li>The App is provided “as is,” without warranties of uninterrupted availability, error-free operation, or fitness for a particular purpose.</li>
    <li>We are not liable for losses caused by improper user inputs, reliance on model outputs, device or network issues, third-party failures, or force majeure.</li>
</ul>

<h2>9. Updates</h2>
<p>We may update this Agreement per laws or business needs; updates will be shown in-app. Continued use means acceptance.</p>

<h2>10. Contact</h2>
<p>For questions or feedback, use the in-app “Service Agreement / Privacy Policy” entry or feedback channel.</p>

